claim.claim-text:
1. An apparatus for heat connecting sections of polymeric tape, comprising: 
a thin elongated welding head for heating the tape sections and provided with a thermostat; 
a pivoting arm for supporting the welding head; 
a substantially flat tubular member for receiving the welding head and the thermostat; and 
a control module mounted ahead of the welding head on the pivoting arm for temperature control.
